metric_description: Average latency for all disk read operations (NOTE: this metric will only be populated for High Scale instances). Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Average latency for all disk write operations (NOTE: this metric will only be populated for High Scale instances). Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Total free disk bytes. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Free disk space as a percentage of the total space. Values are numbers between 0.0 and 100.0. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Count of disk metadata operations (NOTE: this metric will only be populated for High Scale instances). Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
NFS server procedure call count. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Bytes read from disk. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.

metric_display: Time (in milliseconds) spent on read operations
metric_description: Count of milliseconds spent on disk read operations. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Count of disk read operations. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Total used disk bytes. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Used disk space as a percentage of the total space. Values are numbers between 0.0 and 100.0. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Bytes written to disk. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.

metric_display: Time (in milliseconds) spent on write operations
metric_description: Count of milliseconds spent on disk write operations. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
Count of disk write operations. Sampled every 60 seconds. After sampling, data is not visible for up to 180 seconds.
